      "year": 2022,
      "quote": "应该强调的是，以增值价格进行的回购在每一个方面都有利于所有股东。",
      "source": "berkshire_zh/2022-letter-zh.md",
      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/2022-letter.md#p7"
    },
    {
      "year": 2023,
      "quote": "然后——哈利路亚！",
      "source": "berkshire_zh/2023-letter-zh.md",
      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/2023-letter.md#p11"
    },
    {
      "year": 2024,
      "quote": "投资流通股票时，我犯了错更容易纠正。",
      "source": "berkshire_zh/2024-letter-zh.md",
      "jump_link": "./wiki/letters/2024-letter.md#p10"
    }
